    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Chakra Control (Body)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 5 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 17</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You focus Chakra into your body, partially activating your bloodline. Your eyes change in appearance as if the bloodline were active, and if your bloodline can gain the ability to See Chakra, you are capable of doing so while the technique lasts. This does not grant any other benefits, nor does it activate the bloodline or allow you to activate it for free.</p>\n\n\n\n",
